attributes.title: Made my pet lamp die
attributes.review: When I downloaded the app my lamp died. It fell in the floor gasping for air. At first I wasn’t sure what happened to it then I realized it was the app. I am still in tears from this terrible thing. Do not download or it will probably make your too or even worse. My friend told me her painting died from a heart attack shortly after downloading. REMEMBER DO NOT DOWNLOAD!!

attributes.title: Triumphant
attributes.review: I don’t know what all these crazy reviews are talking about. The app downloaded quicker than sneeze and I immediately got a robocall telling me that my soul was being auctioned off in New Jersey for pennies on the dollar to fight public perception and build an army of Covid-eating, electronic, aunts. The supreme leader in his glorious plumes of orange and gold will rise and like a floating poo and the world shall see the three-legged truth of the tripod.
This app hacked my phone and started playing a zoe loverline fan edit video on repeat. I had to put it in the milk to get it to stop. Not good
